  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now available with free Content Update #01!</strong></h2><br>Bigger open world, Utah Beach, improved AI - all for free!</p><br><h1>JOIN US ON DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>United Assault - Normandy '44 is an open world rogue lite FPS set in 1944's depiction of Normandy.<br>You are a US army paratrooper dropped into enemy territory to prepare the D-Day. Your mission objectives vary form destroying Panzer IV tanks, Flak 88 cannons to obtaining secret documents or even liberate an entire town. After completing your objectives, exfiltrate and claim your rewards.<br><br>Higher ranks will unlock new weapons and allow you to customize your start loadout.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15 towns and settlements based on their real world location<br></li><li>Dynamic mission generator<br></li><li>Over 15 authentic weapons<br></li><li>Detailed progression system<br></li><li>Uncover a mysterious secret protected by highly trained german troops<br></li><li>Nvidia DLSS 2.0 support</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now available with free Content Update #01!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Doubled the size of the open world<br></li><li> 4 new Towns<br></li><li> Utah Beach as accessable area<br></li><li> improved AI</li></ul>",
